#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc181"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts181"></a><a class="pts" id="pts24"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.31:5.1"
msgid "“Yato ahaṃ pabbajito,"
msgstr "When I became a monk"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.31:5.2"
msgid "sammāsambuddhasāsane;"
msgstr "In the teaching of the Buddha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.31:5.3"
msgid "Vimuccamāno uggacchiṃ,"
msgstr "Letting go, I rose up;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.31:5.4"
msgid "kāmadhātuṃ upaccagaṃ."
msgstr "I escaped the realm of sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc182"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts182"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.31:6.1"
msgid "Brahmuno pekkhamānassa,"
msgstr "Then, under the supervision of the supreme Buddha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.31:6.2"
msgid "tato cittaṃ vimucci me;"
msgstr "My mind was freed."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.31:6.3"
msgid "Akuppā me vimuttīti,"
msgstr "I know that my freedom is unshakeable,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.31:6.4"
msgid "sabbasaṃyojanakkhayā”ti."
msgstr "Because all fetters have ended."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
